										</iframe>
										</div>
          <p class="posttags">Tags: <a href="http://blog.batchblue.com/tag/second-life/" rel="tag">Second Life</a>, <a href="http://blog.batchblue.com/tag/virtual-office/" rel="tag">virtual office</a></p>

</div> <!-- close #post-65 -->

